#: givefood/templates/public/page.html:78
msgid "About us"
msgstr "maH qoq"

#: givefood/templates/public/about_us.html:25
msgid ""
"\n"
"                <p>Give Food is a UK charity that uses data to highlight "
"local and structural food insecurity, then provides tools to help alleviate "
"it.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>We run the only <a href=\"/needs/\">national public "
"database of food banks</a>, tracking in realtime what they are requesting to "
"have donated.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Working with a wide variety of public and private "
"organisations, including many other charities, we share our data with "
"millions of users each year, helping people learn about and engage with food "
"poverty causes.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>We became a <a href=\"https://register-of-"
"charities.charitycommission.gov.uk/en/charity-search/-/charity-details/"
"5147019\">charity</a> in February 2020, just weeks before the UK entered "
"COVID-19 lockdowns, and since then we've worked with hundreds of local food "
"insecurity alleviation organisations delivering hundreds of tonnes of "
"vitally needed supplies.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>For example, during the pandemic we delivered <a href=\"/"
"2020/#ppe-supplies\">1.2m items of PPE</a> to help keep food banks from "
"Penzance to Lerwick as safe as possible whilst continuing to support their "
"communities.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>We help the public act on food insecurity by using our "
"data to show which food banks are in their parliamentary constituency, and "
"provide a <a href=\"/write/\">tool to easily email their Member of "
"Parliament</a> asking what action they are taking to remedy it.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Our operations are open source and transparent, with "
"almost all of our current and historical <a href=\"https://github.com/"
"givefood/givefood\">code</a> and <a href=\"/api/\">data</a> published, plus "
"<a href=\"https://register-of-charities.charitycommission.gov.uk/charity-"
"search/-/charity-details/5147019/accounts-and-annual-returns\">accounts</a> "
"and <a href=\"/annual-reports/\">annual reports</a> available to view.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Please don't hesitate to contact us with any suggestions, "
"comments, criticism or encouragement.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    <em>The Give Food Trustees</em>\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    <a "
"href=\"mailto:mail@givefood.org.uk\">mail@givefood.org.uk</a>\n"
"                </p>\n"
"\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"                <p>Give Food 'oH SepmeyDaq Soj poHbe'ghach, 'ej Soj "
"poHbe'ghach tI'angbogh De' lo'bogh, UK charity'e'. vaj, 'oH tI'ang, 'ej 'oH "
"QapmeH ghoSmoHbogh janmey je nob.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>maQap: maH neH <a href=\"/needs/\">food bankmey national "
"public database</a> wIrun, realtime wIghItlh, nuq nobmeH poQbogh 'e' "
"wIghovmoH.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>public 'ej private organisationmey law' maQapbogh, latlh "
"charitymey je, maDe' wIshare, Hoch DIS poHmeyDaq, lo'wI'pu' 'uy' law' wIHev, "
"Soj poHbe'ghach Qapmey ghojmoH 'ej ghojmoHmeH Qap wIchenmoH.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>Feb 2020Daq <a href=\"https://register-of-"
"charities.charitycommission.gov.uk/en/charity-search/-/charity-details/"
"5147019\">charity</a> maH, UK COVID-19 lockdownmeyDaq ghoSqa'pu' ret, 'ej "
"vaj, local Soj poHbe'ghach QapmeH organisationmey 'uy' law' maQap, 'ej Soj "
"law' wIghoSmoH, poQqu'bogh supplies law' wIHevmoH.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>chIm, pandemicDaq <a href=\"/2020/#ppe-supplies\">1.2m "
"PPE Dochmey</a> wIHevmoH, Penzancevo' LerwickDaq food bankmey tI'IQmoH, "
"QaptaHbogh 'ej communitymey tI'IQmoHtaH.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>maDe' wIlo' 'ej public ghoSmoH: parliamentary "
"constituencyDaq nuqDaq food bankmey tu'lu' 'e' wI'ang, 'ej <a href=\"/write/"
"\">jan</a> wInob, Member of ParliamentvaD QIn yIghItlhlaH, nuq Qap 'e' "
"yIpoQmoH, Soj poHbe'ghach tI'uchmeH.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>maQap open source 'ej leghlaHbogh, 'ej ma <a "
"href=\"https://github.com/givefood/givefood\">code</a> 'ej <a href=\"/api/"
"\">data</a> HochHom wIpublish, 'ej <a href=\"https://register-of-"
"charities.charitycommission.gov.uk/charity-search/-/charity-details/5147019/"
"accounts-and-annual-returns\">accounts</a> 'ej <a href=\"/annual-reports/"
"\">DIS repmey</a> leghlaH.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>tugh maQelQo' 'e' yIHechQo': yIghItlh, yIja', yIQIch, "
"pagh yIghoSmoH.</p>\n"
"\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    <em>The Give Food Trustees</em>\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    <a "
"href=\"mailto:mail@givefood.org.uk\">mail@givefood.org.uk</a>\n"
"                </p>\n"
"\n"
"            "

